      <description>&lt;p&gt;This page shows the interop helpers that bridge task, async, and synchronous boundaries in FsFlow.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;taskflow-bridges&#34;&gt;TaskFlow bridges&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;//localhost:3000/reference/taskflow/taskflow-fromflow/&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;TaskFlow.fromFlow&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow/TaskFlow.fs#L261&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;//localhost:3000/reference/taskflow/taskflow-fromasyncflow/&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;TaskFlow.fromAsyncFlow&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow/TaskFlow.fs#L264&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;//localhost:3000/reference/taskflow/taskflow-orelsetask/&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;TaskFlow.orElseTask&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow/TaskFlow.fs#L185&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;//localhost:3000/reference/taskflow/taskflow-orelseasync/&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;TaskFlow.orElseAsync&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Turns a pure validation result into a task flow with task-provided failure. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow/TaskFlow.fs#L200&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;//localhost:3000/reference/taskflow/taskflow-orelseflow/&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;TaskFlow.orElseFlow&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow/TaskFlow.fs#L213&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;//localhost:3000/reference/taskflow/taskflow-orelseasyncflow/&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;TaskFlow.orElseAsyncFlow&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow/TaskFlow.fs#L227&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;//localhost:3000/reference/taskflow/taskflow-orelsetaskflow/&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;TaskFlow.orElseTaskFlow&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow/TaskFlow.fs#L245&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;//localhost:3000/reference/flow/flow-providelayer/&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;Flow.provideLayer&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Provides a derived environment from a layer flow to a downstream flow. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow/Flow.fs#L331&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;//localhost:3000/reference/asyncflow/asyncflow-providelayer/&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;AsyncFlow.provideLayer&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Provides a derived environment from a layer flow to a downstream flow. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow/AsyncFlow.fs#L313&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;//localhost:3000/reference/taskflow/taskflow-providelayer/&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;TaskFlow.provideLayer&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Provides a derived environment from a layer flow to a downstream task flow. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow/TaskFlow.fs#L569&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;builder-extensions&#34;&gt;Builder extensions&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;module &lt;code&gt;TaskFlowBuilderExtensions&lt;/code&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow/TaskFlow.fs#L1290&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;module &lt;code&gt;AsyncFlowBuilderExtensions&lt;/code&gt;: [omit] &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow/TaskFlow.fs#L1444&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
